<p>I am trying to build a robot. But a bigger robot than a Raspberry Pi connected to some tiny something as big as a can of black Coke. I am planning to build a robot of a size 1.2-1.5m. I already have chosen some torso, arms and so, but, the problem is the base (bigger wheels, able to cope with weight of 10kg minimum).</p>

