				<p>You use the term "base" as if it is some standard part you just need a bigger version of when in fact that term has no clear definition. It would be helpful if you [edit] your question to include the functionality that you expect from that base. For me, a base might be just a piece of metal that components get attached to. For you, it seems to include motors, wheels and the overall functionality to move the robot around. Please clarify what you want and need. Thanks</p>
