			<div id = "comment-19025" class = "comment">
				<p>At this size I would build something. Build a base of about the right size, out of metal (aluminium or steel angle bolted together) or simply wood if a cheap prototype. Bolt on two heavy duty geared motors (with encoders built in if desired) and find suitable high current motor drivers.  An off the shelf robot base at this sort of size would be quite expensive to buy ready-made.</p>
